<b>Who are we?</b>
<br>
Itzypad is a small community of readers and authors seeking to share their favorite webnovels and original novels to the world. We've been run this community since 2020, and have come a long way since setting out to implement our vision of what a great site should look and feel like. 
<br>
<b>What do we offer</b>
<br>
Itzypad offers a wide range of novels of virtually all conceivale genres, with the exception of erotica story. We feature novels from all across the world.
